<p><strong>D. Report Design</strong></p>
<br />
<p>The system will generate an invoice report. The invoice will contain data about the guest, the booking information, and the billing information gathered from the Reservation and Billing pages and from the third party payments system.  
The report will have a list of every transaction with its respective date, description, and amount. The user will be able to run the report anytime after the payment has been made. He/She will have the option to print and/or email this report. </p>